      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJlqCvkmUSNtszPXp080YyLgqkWXuJ4_9mMLcwjTs7H0Umnv96n_4tDtrRxGff8ako5a7OcdhASWbuWPa3bKQJH3zNZNeYjOteY9jH1svIGJhWCJJw2O3j"
      title: "bankfxapi.com"
    }
    web_documents {
      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEUjLSbtSM_ltseTAze9ThRwU0ByWgQm93qABlgtUyhaqiFmM8auROeMHBAFIUeCnT56ObK_jNbjLN3lYXDbWr7vLB93PJU92ef3u4_Iy08cdXh9V9Pcu9nyS0KYELk-bkdQjrxolU="
      title: "github.io"
    }
    summary: "There are several public APIs that provide exchange rates from the Central Bank of Venezuela (BCV) for various currencies, primarily focusing on the US Dollar (USD) against the Venezuelan Bol\303\255var (VES). While no official BCV API directly publishes rates for USDT (Tether), the BCV\'s official USD exchange rate is generally used as a reference for USDT, given its peg to the US Dollar.\n\nHere are some public API options for obtaining BCV exchange rates, mainly for USD to VES:\n\n*   **BCV (Banco Central de Venezuela) Exchange Rate API by rafnixg.dev**: This API offers real-time and historical exchange rate data for various currencies. It provides endpoints to get the latest exchange rates for a specific currency (e.g., USD) and historical rates for a given date. An API key is required for access, and there\'s a rate limit of 100 requests per minute. The base URL for the API is `https://bcv-api.rafnixg.dev/v1/`[1][2]. For example, to get the latest USD rate, you would use an endpoint like `GET /exchange-rates/latest/USD`[1].\n*   **BCV Today API**: This service provides a public JSON API with the official Banco Central de Venezuela rates for the US dollar, Euro, Chinese Yuan, Turkish Lira, and Russian Ruble against the Bol\303\255var. Users can check current values and daily history[3].\n*   **BankFxApi**: This API offers exchange rates directly from the Banco Central de Venezuela. It provides an API endpoint to retrieve rates, including USD, which are cached for optimal performance. The data is provided for informational purposes[4].\n*   **api-bcvcurs.herokuapp.com**: This RESTful API retrieves BCV currency values directly from the official bcv.org.ve website. It includes endpoints for currencies like the dollar, euro, ruble, lira, and yuan[5].\n\nIt\'s important to note that USDT is a stablecoin pegged to the US Dollar. Therefore, when looking for \"BCV USDT\" exchange rates, the most relevant and officially published rate from the BCV will be the USD to VES exchange rate[3].\n\nSources:\n[1] [publicapi.dev](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHD9UjrG1wZGJeAEkM5rukGusiPoIFHnQWJGiPQifJ_CDpG1I2pauCcSxJjs6lWVkT4bJ4u6DIPPbeqq81kGT3i0elwigSUtZG18kKChvM45YZomXefMgSYJC3_B8FWsE3Qiw0t0d-nwb2Tr-sE087LBStovoLgsO-waUDZT_MEuqQ=)\n[2] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHc1B5v34kz0bg9YWTsODi4E2ZGq3e0NiPDuvVglVWPgv4cgjbrxRjJyz_j7kabuB8poADxtnn9z36PFrVtJN1VsQYqiHvM5wOzzT82zXCteFbIhdxMOizH8rJa_GY=)\n[3] [bcv.today](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQH4HY6G7RxSq9xgcYjcuCBPjavkceQ4qkf98UvaNFwxh6DB8ty601wQZXEZxihRAE19sFXyFeUmaYWqNrY_Kox7llJMNEfyXLnyWKRnPm__gg==)\n[4] [bankfxapi.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGJlqCvkmUSNtszPXp080YyLgqkWXuJ4_9mMLcwjTs7H0Umnv96n_4tDtrRxGff8ako5a7OcdhASWbuWPa3bKQJH3zNZNeYjOteY9jH1svIGJhWCJJw2O3j)\n[5] [github.io](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQEUjLSbtSM_ltseTAze9ThRwU0ByWgQm93qABlgtUyhaqiFmM8auROeMHBAFIUeCnT56ObK_jNbjLN3lYXDbWr7vLB93PJU92ef3u4_Iy08cdXh9V9Pcu9nyS0KYELk-bkdQjrxolU=)"
    search_type: SEARCH_WEB_TYPE_WEB
  }
}
